{
  "texts": [
    "For each type of NRAS and KRAS mutations, variant allele frequencies (VAFs) are also shown.",
    "The lines of the box represent 25% quantile, median, and 75% quantile.",
    "The upper whisker represents the higher value of maxima or 1.5 x IQR, and the lower whisker represents the lower value of minima or 1.5 x IQR.",
    "Dots represent outliers.",
    "*q < 0.05, blue: exclusive, red: enriched)."
  ]
}